ed="T" n="0759c19"/><persName key="A010192">釋香育</persName>，姓李氏，<placeName key="PL000000023001">濟陰</placeName>人也。父為<placeName key="PL000000021539">兗<anchor xml:id="beg0759007"/>州<anchor xml:id="end0759007"/></placeName>掾。<persName key="A010192">育</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0759c20"/>有道性，常研習《莊》《老》，根器<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1418"/>奮發。俄於釋典<lb
ed="T" n="0759c21"/>留神，決捐俗態。趨<placeName key="PL000000003030">滄州安定寺</placeName><persName key="A010194">智元<roleName>律師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0759c22"/>所，乞求削染。滿足戒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g33"/>後，精力律學，垂欲卒<lb
ed="T" n="0759c23"/>業。一旦辭<ref type="person" target="#A010194">師</ref>觀遊聖跡，陟<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>，登<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>，或<lb
ed="T" n="0759c24"/>入巖阿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1419"/>，或棲樹下，末至<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>。後參預<persName key="A009582">秀<roleName>師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0759c25"/>盛化，夙心相契，擊節<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1420"/>希聲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1421"/>。<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>問<ref type="person" target="#A010192">之</ref>，<persName key="A010192">育</persName>答密<lb
ed="T" n="0759c26"/>若隱書<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1423"/>，一皆開釋。<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>默異<ref type="person" target="#A010192">之</ref>。在叢眾間，多<lb
ed="T" n="0759c27"/>歷年所，洞徹心源，則辭<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>去。入<placeName key="PL000000027459">富水大佛<lb
ed="T" n="0759c28"/>山</placeName>，勁節安禪，卯前一食。州將<persName key="A010196">韓閏</persName>篤欽其道，<lb
ed="T" n="0759c29"/>堅召出山。<persName key="A010192">育</persName>稱疾而已。因是黑白之眾渴<pb ed="T" n="0760a" xml:id="T50.2061.0760a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0760a01"/>仰歸依，<persName key="A010196">韓<roleName>使君</roleName></persName>輜車繼運，供施交駢，樹造法<lb
ed="T" n="0760a02"/>堂，嚴飾奇麗，時來問道。<persName key="A010196">韓<roleName>侯</roleName></persName>問：「佛法已後<lb
ed="T" n="0760a03"/>事如何？」答云：「如同太虛，委在有力。」<persName key="A010196">韓<roleName>侯</roleName></persName>欽<lb
ed="T" n="0760a04"/>尚。徒眾常有千計，賢、不肖駮雜<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1314"/>而居，往往<lb
ed="T" n="0760a05"/>聞有不測之僧預其聽受焉。一旦說法次<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1422"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0760a06"/>告眾曰：「善哉是會，遭遇者艱。須決所疑，無<lb
ed="T" n="0760a07"/>遣虛度。」命水滌盥，端坐而化，春秋七十有<lb
ed="T" n="0760a08"/>三矣。</p>
